datasets.name: dataset_2
queryLines: SELECT DATE_TRUNC('DAY', `Event Date Time`) AS `Daily Event Date`, MEASURE(`New Devices`) AS `New Devices`, SUM(MEASURE(`New Devices`)) OVER (ORDER BY DATE_TRUNC('DAY', `Event Date Time`) ROWS UNBOUNDED PRECEDING) AS `Cumulative New Devices` FROM `workspace.default.hpx_events_model` GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('DAY', `Event Date Time`) ORDER BY `Daily Event Date`

fields.name: Cumulative New Devices
fields.expression: SUM(MEASURE(`New Devices`)) OVER (ORDER BY DATE_TRUNC('DAY', `Event Date Time`) ROWS UNBOUNDED PRECEDING)

frame.title: New and Cumulative Devices Over Time
